Bartok is a download manager for various filesharing sites (Megaupload,etc). It
also supports searching link aggregator.

Bartok is composed of two components. A daemon and a user front end.

The daemon is launched by:

bartok.pl -d

Then adding a file to download is accomplished with:

bartok.pl --add url

Note: running bartok.pl with no arguments will give a more detailed explanation
of parameters.
